22:16.636 --> 22:20.438
¶ the whole world stops
and drops you ¶

22:20.440 --> 22:23.240
¶ like you're nothin' ¶

22:25.611 --> 22:28.979
¶ how do you make amends ¶

22:28.981 --> 22:34.051
¶ for all the goodbyes
that might have been? ¶

