[ cadence crying ]

23:16.496 --> 23:18.195
Shh, shh, shh.

23:18.197 --> 23:19.730
Sweet girl.

23:19.732 --> 23:21.098
Call me back, avery.

23:21.100 --> 23:23.167
[ sighs ]

23:23.169 --> 23:24.402
Everything okay in here?

23:24.404 --> 23:25.836
Oh, she's just teething,

23:25.838 --> 23:28.372
And she won't take the ring
that I stuck in the freezer.

23:28.374 --> 23:29.940
Here. Try this.

23:29.942 --> 23:31.442
Come here.
[ fussing ]

23:31.444 --> 23:33.778
Hey.
[ laughing ] hey.

23:33.780 --> 23:35.679
Here you go.
Want to try that?

23:35.681 --> 23:37.615
[ sighs ]
yeah.

23:37.617 --> 23:39.183
[ chuckles ]

23:39.185 --> 23:40.785
My niece anna's gums
were too sensitive

23:40.787 --> 23:42.686
For all the cold stuff
when she was teething.

23:42.688 --> 23:44.622
Wooden spoon was the only thing
that worked.

23:44.624 --> 23:46.123
Huh?
There you go.

23:46.125 --> 23:48.492
You are
just full of surprises.

23:57.103 --> 23:59.537
[ woman speaking indistinctly
on p.A. ]

24:02.241 --> 24:04.275
Something I can
help you with, sarge?
Yeah.

24:04.277 --> 24:07.912
You know, they say a father's
job is to protect his child.

24:07.914 --> 24:09.647
Why is it that you're always
hurting yours, huh?

24:09.649 --> 24:10.948
Excuse me?

24:10.950 --> 24:12.049
What in the hell
were you thinking

24:12.051 --> 24:13.984
Even starting this crusade
of yours?

24:13.986 --> 24:15.619
I did it
to help out a good kid,

24:15.621 --> 24:17.621
Maybe change some minds
for the better.

24:17.623 --> 24:19.256
You know what --
I watch the news,

24:19.258 --> 24:20.724
And I don't see
that it's going very well.

24:20.726 --> 24:22.293
No, it's not.

24:22.295 --> 24:24.595
In fact, I got protesters
outside my office,

24:24.597 --> 24:26.997
I'm losing fans by the day,
hemorrhaging cash.

24:26.999 --> 24:29.066
Well, I hope that singer
of yours appreciates it,

24:29.068 --> 24:31.268
Considering that you were
fighting his fights for him

24:31.270 --> 24:34.305
While your son was here
getting his head kicked in!

24:34.307 --> 24:36.307
You think you can
make me feel worse? Is that it?

24:36.309 --> 24:38.442
I was just trying to do
the right thing, damn it!

24:38.444 --> 24:39.577
I was just trying to --

