26:57.817 --> 27:00.050
Is that what<i> you</i> want?

27:01.220 --> 27:03.153
You think about it,
babe.

27:16.836 --> 27:17.601
[ cheers and applause ]

27:17.603 --> 27:19.203
Thank you.

27:21.674 --> 27:24.742
Fantastic. If anything,
I set expectations too<i> low.</i>

27:24.744 --> 27:26.076
-Perfect, kiddo.
-Thank you.

27:26.078 --> 27:27.645
Thanks.
-Perfect. Come here.

27:27.647 --> 27:29.647
Rod phillips from iheart radio
wants to meet you.

27:29.649 --> 27:31.415
Come on.
Okay.

27:31.417 --> 27:32.750
Hey, where's avery?

27:32.752 --> 27:34.184
I don't know.

27:36.022 --> 27:37.521
Hey. [ sighs ]

27:37.523 --> 27:39.623
