I was onstage.

27:39.625 --> 27:40.758
Is cadence okay?

27:40.760 --> 27:41.759
Yeah, she's fine.

27:41.761 --> 27:43.427
She was fussy,
like you said she was,

27:43.429 --> 27:46.030
