got her to calm down.

27:46.032 --> 27:47.698
Noah did?
Oh, he's so sweet.

27:47.700 --> 27:49.266
Oh, that's great.

27:49.268 --> 27:52.002
Yeah,
glad he could help out.

27:52.004 --> 27:53.504
Hope you two
are having fun.

27:53.506 --> 27:54.638
We are.

27:54.640 --> 27:56.473
In fact, I should probably
hang up and get back to it.

27:56.475 --> 27:58.042
Yeah.

27:58.044 --> 27:59.543
