couldn't care less about me?

37:37.055 --> 37:38.221
Hey.

37:38.223 --> 37:40.423
Of course
highway 65 cares about you.

37:40.425 --> 37:42.092
I mean, look.
Look at this.

37:42.094 --> 37:44.561
Yeah, but I just feel
like crying.

37:44.563 --> 37:46.096
It's just, tonight was
supposed to be perfect,

37:46.098 --> 37:48.064
