Okay?

37:50.402 --> 37:51.935
Come on.

37:51.937 --> 37:53.570
I'm gonna take you out,

37:53.572 --> 37:57.607
And we're gonna turn it
all around, starting right now.

37:57.609 --> 37:59.142
What about cadence?

38:00.112 --> 38:01.645
