39:57.262 --> 39:59.028
I just don't think
we have the connection

39:59.030 --> 40:01.598
That I need to feel
right now.

40:03.402 --> 40:08.004
I guess the fantasy's
better than the reality, huh?

40:12.611 --> 40:15.345
At least we tried,
right?

40:23.021 --> 40:25.755
You don't have to leave.

40:25.757 --> 40:27.857
I know.

40:27.859 --> 40:30.026
But I-I probably should.

40:41.373 --> 40:42.772
How bad is it?

40:42.774 --> 40:44.240
Oh,
it's barely noticeable.

40:44.242 --> 40:45.275
[ both chuckle ]

40:45.277 --> 40:46.276
[ cellphone ringing ]

40:46.278 --> 40:47.877
Hold on a sec.

40:47.879 --> 40:49.279
Let me grab this.

40:49.281 --> 40:50.480
Hey, will.

40:50.482 --> 40:52.382
Hey. How's colt?

40:52.384 --> 40:54.651
Oh, he's gonna be all right.
He's a tough kid.

40:54.653 --> 40:55.919
How'd the radio spot go?

40:55.921 --> 40:57.153
It went good.

40:57.155 --> 40:58.388
Apparently,
word about it spread,

40:58.390 --> 41:00.423
Because it lit a fire
under cynthia davis again.

41:00.425 --> 41:03.493
Oh, you know what? [ sighs ]
don't you worry about her.

41:03.495 --> 41:06.496
Some people got so much hate
in them, it's just not worth it.

41:06.498 --> 41:08.398
Actually, um...

41:08.400 --> 41:10.600
I made a decision.

41:10.602 --> 41:13.369
I want to go on the show --
take her on face-to-face.

41:14.806 --> 41:16.272
Okay.

41:16.274 --> 41:18.942
I'm, uh, not sure
