41:22.581 --> 41:24.514
No, you've done so much
for me, luke,

41:24.516 --> 41:28.251
And I am truly grateful,
but...

41:28.253 --> 41:30.053
It's time for<i> me</i>
to take from here.

41:31.089 --> 41:33.656
Well, all right, then.

41:33.658 --> 41:35.558
Go get 'er, son.

